title: Weds Post Show (03-23-22)
itunes:title: Weds Post Show (03-23-22)
description:
Bobby starts by talking about a woman with “biggest breasts in the US” who wants them removed. John Travolta now has his pilot license to fly a 737. Bobby shares a texting pet peeves he has when someone just asks him ‘if you’re busy on a certain day’. Bobby teases a new podcast idea.
